    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require schools to have gender-neutral uniform policies",
        "additional_details": "So many school uniform policies fail to meet the needs of non-binary students. People should comfortable and confident in their school uniform.",
        "background": "Schools should be required to set uniform policies that are gender neutral, so that people can decide to wear whatever items of school uniform they feel most comfortable in. This is especially important for people who are non-binary.",
